at a general principle, formulated in terms of many-body\nHilbert space concepts, is at the core of the occurrence of $T$-linear\nresistivity in a wide range of systems, and precisely translates $T$-linear\nresistivity into a notion of energy scale invariance far beyond what is\ntypically associated with quantum critical points.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Jun 2021 18:00:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 1 Mar 2022 23:50:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-11"}
