E-MS-QP waveform enables simultaneous\ninterference-free sensing and communication, whilst inheriting all the merits\nfrom MS-QP sequences. Numerical results validate the superiority of the\nproposed waveforms regarding the communication and sensing performances,\nhardware cost as well as flexibility of the resource allocation between the\ndual functions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Jun 2021 02:08:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 25 Jul 2022 02:43:58 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 26 Dec 2022 08:30:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-27"}
