trumental conditions along the mission and the\ngeneration of mean spectra from a number of observations of the same source.\nThe output of this model provides the internal mean spectra, not as a sampled\nfunction (flux and wavelength), but as a linear combination of basis functions,\nalthough sampled spectra can easily be derived from them.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Jun 2021 11:04:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 30 Jun 2021 13:40:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-18"}
