owed how the local fairness of a preprocessing stage composes in\nthe global fairness of the pipeline. We used the fairness composition to choose\nappropriate downstream transformer that mitigates unfairness in the machine\nlearning pipeline.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Jun 2021 20:39:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 14 Jun 2021 17:22:22 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 18 Jun 2021 06:35:12 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 8 Jul 2021 17:51:55 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Tue, 20 Jul 2021 00:12:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-21"}
